title: Ceiling Wall, 1905–15
inscribed: Printed in selvedge: "S. A. Maxwell & Co. New York & Chicago 2329" "Exclusive Design"
description:
Alternating medallions inside yellow rose wreaths and white flower wreaths with petal-shaped vining tendrils. Ground is light green. Printed in white, silver mica, green, yellow, and brown. 
Printed in selvedge: "S. A. Maxwell & Co. New York & Chicago 2329" "Exclusive Design"

Ceiling Wall, 1905–15.
1905–15. Machine-printed on paper, mica, liquid. Gift of Victorian Collectibles. 1979-91-1219.
